50|$|Ganesh Prasad Singh (born 1 July 1947) was {{a member}} of the 14th Lok Sabha of India. He {{represented}} the Jahanabad constituency of Bihar and is a member of the Rashtriya Janata Dal (RJD) political party. He has supported the view that <b>voluntary</b> <b>repatriation</b> of refugees is the best and most durable solution, specifically in the case of Afghan refugees.|$|E
